1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 66 =

20
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:40,300
Yuanheng once told me

21
00:01:40,980 --> 00:01:42,580
he wanted to stay with Princess.

22
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:44,260
She meant the most

23
00:01:44,260 --> 00:01:45,180
to him.

24
00:01:45,180 --> 00:01:45,820
Fine.

25
00:01:46,220 --> 00:01:47,540
I kept the past

26
00:01:47,540 --> 00:01:48,460
all to myself,

27
00:01:49,820 --> 00:01:50,820
but I just found out

28
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:52,660
that he had already been exiled.

29
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:55,340
Mr. Zhang,

30
00:01:55,620 --> 00:01:56,940
there must be something you can do.

31
00:01:57,580 --> 00:01:59,020
Fake his death,

32
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:00,620
bring him out

33
00:02:00,980 --> 00:02:03,620
so that my brother and I can reunite.

34
00:02:04,940 --> 00:02:06,100
I can’t do that.

35
00:02:08,940 --> 00:02:10,220
Why can’t you?

36
00:02:10,860 --> 00:02:12,580
Nobody here would care if a slave

37
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:14,500
in the palace in Luoyang is missing.

38
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:17,260
Huaiji...

39
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:20,780
Huaiji isn’t any other slave.

40
00:02:21,380 --> 00:02:23,780
If anything bad happens to him,

41
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:25,420
Princess will collapse.

42
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:28,060
If they care about Princess,

43
00:02:28,580 --> 00:02:30,180
why not give him back to her?

44
00:02:31,460 --> 00:02:33,500
If the imperial family’s reputation weighs more...

45
00:02:33,900 --> 00:02:35,020
His Majesty doesn’t love her daughter

46
00:02:35,020 --> 00:02:36,140
too much.

47
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:36,900
Enough!

48
00:02:38,940 --> 00:02:39,780
Liang Yuansheng,

49
00:02:40,860 --> 00:02:42,060
are you seeking death?

50
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:44,580
Sir, you know

51
00:02:45,140 --> 00:02:46,700
he’s my only brother.

52
00:02:47,260 --> 00:02:48,620
If I can’t save him,

53
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:51,180
my...my business, my life

54
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:52,060
all don’t matter anymore.

55
00:02:52,420 --> 00:02:53,140
And...

56
00:02:53,980 --> 00:02:55,180
And my brother only ended up like this

57
00:02:55,180 --> 00:02:56,740
because of those officials

58
00:02:56,740 --> 00:02:57,700
and His Majesty.

59
00:02:57,700 --> 00:02:58,540
What did you say?

60
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:02,060
I fought against invaders, corrupted officials.

61
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:04,220
I’m a hero.

62
00:03:04,340 --> 00:03:06,340
The court owes my family!

63
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:21,940
= A few months later =

64
00:03:21,940 --> 00:03:23,100
Can you carve

65
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:24,900
nicer clothes for her,

66
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:25,660
please?

67
00:03:25,900 --> 00:03:27,900
She’ll be my daughter.

68
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:30,460
Sure.

69
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:34,500
So what do you want her to be?

70
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:37,620
I want her to have babies.

71
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:41,020
I mean

72
00:03:41,100 --> 00:03:42,540
what you want her to do?

73
00:03:43,100 --> 00:03:44,420
Have babies.

74
00:03:44,740 --> 00:03:45,900
Two babies.

75
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:47,180
A boy

76
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:48,260
and a girl.

77
00:03:54,020 --> 00:03:55,100
I mean

78
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:57,340
whether you want her to be Chief of Styling,

79
00:03:58,060 --> 00:03:58,700
Medicine,

80
00:03:58,700 --> 00:04:01,180
Clothes or Etiquette in the future?

81
00:04:02,340 --> 00:04:04,140
I want her to be a mother.

82
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:05,940
That’s what I like the most

83
00:04:06,060 --> 00:04:07,740
and so does she.

84
00:04:21,700 --> 00:04:22,460
Mr. Zhang.

85
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:36,420
Pack up

86
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:37,860
and go back to the Capital with me.

87
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:39,580
Don’t let others know.

88
00:05:04,580 --> 00:05:06,620
Maoze pays respects to Madam Shang.

89
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:10,620
I don’t deserve that title.

90
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:16,620
Madam, do you have messages for His Majesty?

91
00:05:19,780 --> 00:05:20,860
At first,

92
00:05:21,180 --> 00:05:22,820
I hoped that he’d forgive me

93
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,420
and take me back.

94
00:05:25,980 --> 00:05:26,740
Later,

95
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:28,740
I wished him to still remember me.

96
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:31,420
But now,

97
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:35,460
I’m enjoying peace.

98
00:05:36,300 --> 00:05:37,540
I’ve found my own life.

99
00:05:39,900 --> 00:05:40,700
Maoze,

100
00:05:42,020 --> 00:05:43,060
I rejoice

101
00:05:43,380 --> 00:05:45,180
to see old acquaintances

102
00:05:46,300 --> 00:05:47,300
from the Capital before I die.

103
00:05:48,060 --> 00:05:48,820
But

104
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:51,940
please don’t mention me to His Majesty.

105
00:06:53,780 --> 00:06:55,020
Stay in the palace for now.

106
00:06:55,980 --> 00:06:57,980
When Princess comes in to pay respects,

107
00:06:58,180 --> 00:06:59,740
you two can meet.

108
00:07:00,660 --> 00:07:02,300
Let her know you’re fine

109
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:04,500
but that’s it.

110
00:07:05,060 --> 00:07:06,420
You can’t be together

111
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:07,980
as before.

112
00:07:10,140 --> 00:07:11,740
Thank you, Your Majesty and Your Highness.

113
00:07:13,780 --> 00:07:15,740
You can’t work at Madam Miao’s chamber, either.

114
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:17,820
Officer Deng will arrange

115
00:07:18,220 --> 00:07:19,540
a room for you.

116
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:22,340
Give me some time

117
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:23,420
to find you a new post.

118
00:07:24,700 --> 00:07:26,620
To avoid the Censorate’s attention,

119
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:28,300
your position

120
00:07:29,220 --> 00:07:30,420
won’t be too high.

121
00:07:36,020 --> 00:07:36,940
Princess...

122
00:07:40,620 --> 00:07:42,540
I promised her that you’d come back

123
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:46,060
and asked her to go back to her mansion.

124
00:07:47,340 --> 00:07:48,420
She’ll come to the palace

125
00:07:48,980 --> 00:07:50,220
on the Double Ninth Day

126
00:07:52,220 --> 00:07:54,180
when you two can meet at Empress’s chamber.

127
00:07:58,740 --> 00:07:59,940
Thank you, Your Majesty.

128
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:04,100
But I only wish

129
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:06,220
to see her from afar

130
00:08:06,220 --> 00:08:07,620
that day.

131
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:10,260
We don’t need to be too close.

132
00:08:16,420 --> 00:08:18,500
Are you afraid you’ll lose control of yourself

133
00:08:18,700 --> 00:08:20,300
in front of her

134
00:08:21,740 --> 00:08:23,900
or become embarrassed

135
00:08:24,100 --> 00:08:25,220
with Empress there.

136
00:08:36,780 --> 00:08:38,420
I don’t want to see Princess’s tears.

137
00:08:55,620 --> 00:08:56,540
You may leave.

138
00:09:13,700 --> 00:09:16,940
= Hall of Peace =
= Double Ninth Festival =

139
00:09:17,940 --> 00:09:19,100
Rumors officials spreading

140
00:09:19,700 --> 00:09:21,260
about selecting the Crown Prince

141
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:23,820
put strain on Zongshi.

142
00:09:25,220 --> 00:09:26,580
He’s unwell already

143
00:09:27,420 --> 00:09:28,420
and sensitive.

144
00:09:30,060 --> 00:09:31,700
= Gao Taotao =
Now, he refuses to go out

145
00:09:32,420 --> 00:09:33,420
or see anyone.

146
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:36,540
I’m here today

147
00:09:38,380 --> 00:09:39,940
to apologize to you and His Majesty

148
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:41,300
on his behalf.

149
00:09:42,540 --> 00:09:45,060
He’s too sick

150
00:09:46,420 --> 00:09:48,140
to attend the Double Ninth Banquet.

151
00:09:50,460 --> 00:09:52,100
Take good care of him

152
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:55,060
and comfort him as much as you can.

153
00:09:56,300 --> 00:09:58,180
Don’t let him think too much.

154
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:01,260
His Majesty has his reasons

155
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:03,380
for the decisions he makes.

156
00:10:04,740 --> 00:10:06,300
He never acts rashly.

157
00:10:08,140 --> 00:10:10,540
You raised Zongshi for a while when he was little

158
00:10:11,700 --> 00:10:12,580
and you knew

159
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:15,100
he was here twice.

160
00:10:15,940 --> 00:10:17,700
During the ins and outs,

161
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:21,100
he suffered quite a lot.

162
00:10:22,820 --> 00:10:23,580
Right now,

163
00:10:25,420 --> 00:10:27,260
he’s desperate to be out of the hot water

164
00:10:28,780 --> 00:10:29,740
so that our family

165
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:31,220
can have a peaceful life.

166
00:10:33,860 --> 00:10:34,740
Your Highness,

167
00:10:37,260 --> 00:10:38,940
I swear this is my genuine thought.

168
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:42,140
Can you

169
00:10:44,780 --> 00:10:46,140
ask His Majesty

170
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:51,260
to allow us to leave the Capital?

171
00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:57,060
Taotao,

172
00:10:59,300 --> 00:11:00,380
I do know

173
00:11:01,540 --> 00:11:02,740
this golden chair

174
00:11:03,300 --> 00:11:05,820
that countless people are dying to grab

175
00:11:06,180 --> 00:11:07,540
even if it’s beyond their reach,

176
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:09,660
is too heavy.

177
00:11:12,020 --> 00:11:13,220
As for

178
00:11:14,780 --> 00:11:16,060
the owner of it,

179
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:19,900
if it doesn’t belong to you,

180
00:11:21,020 --> 00:11:21,940
then you can’t have it

181
00:11:23,060 --> 00:11:23,980
no matter how hard you try.

182
00:11:26,380 --> 00:11:27,380
But if it does,

183
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:31,460
you can’t get rid of it

184
00:11:32,420 --> 00:11:34,220
as you wish.

185
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:37,300
But...

186
00:11:38,380 --> 00:11:40,020
Where are Zhongke and Zhongzhen?

187
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:44,860
They went to see Huirou.

188
00:11:50,420 --> 00:11:51,780
If she had a choice,

189
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:54,700
I guess

190
00:11:55,620 --> 00:11:56,700
she’d rather be a commoner.

191
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:09,980
Huirou

192
00:12:11,300 --> 00:12:13,060
used to be the most fortunate girl.

193
00:12:14,780 --> 00:12:17,580
But good fortune can turn bad.

194
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:20,460
When that happens,

195
00:12:21,700 --> 00:12:23,620
we should minimize its impact

196
00:12:24,100 --> 00:12:25,580
to improve the situation.

197
00:12:28,020 --> 00:12:29,220
Saying “would rather”

198
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:31,020
is of no use.

199
00:12:36,460 --> 00:12:37,580
Zhongke...

200
00:12:37,580 --> 00:12:38,340
Sister,

201
00:12:38,340 --> 00:12:40,420
Zhongke spilled my rose perfume

202
00:12:40,420 --> 00:12:41,780
you gave me.

203
00:12:41,780 --> 00:12:43,780
He used the bottle to catch fish.

204
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:44,860
Zhongke...

205
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:48,380
There was no perfume left in the bottle,

206
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:49,700
so I took it.

207
00:12:49,900 --> 00:12:52,260
No! The bottle was full.

208
00:12:54,220 --> 00:12:55,780
It was just some perfume.

209
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:57,220
Let it go.

210
00:12:59,980 --> 00:13:01,740
I can give you another bottle.

211
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:02,900
Now?

212
00:13:02,900 --> 00:13:04,700
You’ve brought it with you?

213
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:07,380
Pour it.

214
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:09,540
Here it is.

215
00:13:11,020 --> 00:13:13,540
Look. Isn’t it like a rose?

216
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:14,500
Yes.

217
00:13:15,340 --> 00:13:17,380
Sister, where’s the rose perfume?

218
00:13:18,900 --> 00:13:19,620
Yes.

219
00:13:20,660 --> 00:13:22,380
Put it in carefully.

220
00:13:22,860 --> 00:13:24,060
There are rose petals in the water,

221
00:13:24,060 --> 00:13:25,460
so this is the rose perfume.

222
00:13:31,340 --> 00:13:32,780
I’ll go pick a willow branch

223
00:13:32,780 --> 00:13:34,460
to make a chaplet for Piggy.

224
00:14:05,020 --> 00:14:05,940
Aunt!

225
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:42,740
Princess, as you saw,

226
00:14:44,020 --> 00:14:45,220
Huaiji is fine.

227
00:14:50,900 --> 00:14:52,100
Father won’t give him

228
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,380
back to me, will he?

229
00:15:05,180 --> 00:15:06,500
Did Huirou see Huaiji?

230
00:15:08,340 --> 00:15:09,380
Only a glimpse.

231
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:12,580
She didn’t cry or make a scene.

232
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:13,940
She left before the curfew

233
00:15:14,860 --> 00:15:17,780
and went back to her mansion.

234
00:15:23,340 --> 00:15:24,300
Ask Maoze

235
00:15:24,620 --> 00:15:26,860
to go check on her later.

236
00:15:42,180 --> 00:15:43,820
Did Taotao say anything to you?

237
00:15:45,900 --> 00:15:46,900
Nothing new

238
00:15:48,940 --> 00:15:49,860
other than begging you

239
00:15:50,300 --> 00:15:52,220
to give Zongshi a post outside the Capital

240
00:15:52,900 --> 00:15:54,260
so that they can be away from this mess.

241
00:15:58,620 --> 00:15:59,700
Do you believe her?

242
00:16:02,980 --> 00:16:04,180
I don’t know.

243
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:07,140
I’m not her,

244
00:16:08,340 --> 00:16:09,700
so I don’t know

245
00:16:10,220 --> 00:16:11,740
what she really thinks.

246
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:18,460
What about you?

247
00:16:24,940 --> 00:16:26,220
I first fell in love

248
00:16:28,140 --> 00:16:29,260
with the man

249
00:16:31,420 --> 00:16:32,780
who was a young

250
00:16:35,100 --> 00:16:36,580
and benevolent emperor.

251
00:16:40,140 --> 00:16:41,380
Zhao Zhen and Your Majesty

252
00:16:44,220 --> 00:16:45,580
are a whole.

253
00:16:52,780 --> 00:16:53,780
Back then,

254
00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:57,100
I dreamed all day

255
00:17:00,500 --> 00:17:01,820
of becoming a man

256
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:05,620
so that I could be a soldier or a scholar

257
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:09,140
to assist you in building a great empire.

258
00:17:12,380 --> 00:17:13,300
Later,

259
00:17:15,140 --> 00:17:17,100
when I was actually with you,

260
00:17:19,100 --> 00:17:20,700
I realized

261
00:17:22,780 --> 00:17:24,020
in your heart,

262
00:17:25,420 --> 00:17:26,540
nothing was more important

263
00:17:27,740 --> 00:17:29,220
than this nation and the people.

264
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:32,860
I understood

265
00:17:35,100 --> 00:17:36,260
that only if the state was thriving

266
00:17:37,940 --> 00:17:39,500
could you be relieved.

267
00:17:42,820 --> 00:17:44,180
And so could

268
00:17:46,980 --> 00:17:48,220
my Zhao Zhen.

269
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:54,180
So to me,

270
00:17:56,540 --> 00:17:58,220
the state matters the most.

271
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:29,420
This soup tastes good.

272
00:18:30,420 --> 00:18:31,380
Have some yourself.

273
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:36,980
Zongshi

274
00:18:37,820 --> 00:18:39,300
is the most intelligent and diligent one

275
00:18:39,900 --> 00:18:41,660
among his peers.

276
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:43,500
He’s also upright.

277
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:46,380
But

278
00:18:47,220 --> 00:18:48,300
I always feel

279
00:18:48,700 --> 00:18:50,220
he lacks flexibility

280
00:18:50,740 --> 00:18:52,100
and can be too stubborn sometimes.

281
00:18:57,220 --> 00:18:57,980
Forget it.

282
00:19:01,300 --> 00:19:02,900
Even if Zuixinglai grew up,

283
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:05,940
he might not turn out better than Zongshi.

284
00:19:07,940 --> 00:19:09,980
Even if I had other sons,

285
00:19:10,900 --> 00:19:12,060
I’d have little time to teach them.

286
00:19:31,776 --> 00:19:41,346
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

287
00:19:42,530 --> 00:19:51,083
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

288
00:19:53,753 --> 00:19:58,640
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

289
00:19:59,460 --> 00:20:03,586
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

290
00:20:05,093 --> 00:20:10,566
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

291
00:20:10,566 --> 00:20:15,540
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

292
00:20:38,780 --> 00:20:39,860
His Majesty is still resting.

293
00:20:39,860 --> 00:20:40,980
What’s with the rush?

294
00:20:41,260 --> 00:20:42,260
I need to see His Majesty now.

295
00:20:42,260 --> 00:20:43,340
Zhang Maoze asked me to come.

296
00:20:43,340 --> 00:20:44,620
Princess, Princess...

297
00:20:45,660 --> 00:20:46,540
What’s happening to Huirou?

298
00:20:46,820 --> 00:20:48,900
She...she’s setting her room on fire.

299
00:20:50,620 --> 00:20:51,380
Where’s she?

300
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:52,860
Where’s Huirou?

301
00:20:53,940 --> 00:20:56,140
Order Imperial Guards to rescue her.

302
00:20:56,500 --> 00:20:58,100
Take Huaiji to her mansion.

303
00:21:28,020 --> 00:21:28,700
Your Majesty.

304
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:30,500
How is Huirou?

305
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:32,100
Don’t worry, Your Majesty.

306
00:21:32,540 --> 00:21:34,780
Huaiji already escorted Princess to a safe place.

307
00:21:39,460 --> 00:21:40,180
Good.

308
00:21:41,380 --> 00:21:42,100
That’s good.

309
00:21:54,740 --> 00:21:55,700
Help me tidy up.

310
00:21:56,220 --> 00:21:57,700
I have a meeting at the Hall of Politics.

311
00:21:59,460 --> 00:22:00,940
You should take the morning off.

312
00:22:01,540 --> 00:22:02,900
We can ask Madam Miao

313
00:22:02,900 --> 00:22:04,940
to summon Huirou to the palace to stay for a while.

314
00:22:05,420 --> 00:22:06,260
No.

315
00:22:08,540 --> 00:22:09,460
The fire in her mansion

316
00:22:09,460 --> 00:22:10,620
will surely raise discussions.

317
00:22:10,980 --> 00:22:12,220
If I cancel the meeting,

318
00:22:12,460 --> 00:22:13,780
it’ll only make this matter look worse.

319
00:22:14,620 --> 00:22:16,780
Besides, I’m scheduled to meet Sima Guang today.

320
00:22:17,140 --> 00:22:18,700
If I don’t show up,

321
00:22:18,940 --> 00:22:20,420
he’ll add more charges to Huirou.

322
00:22:22,580 --> 00:22:23,540
I’m fine.

323
00:22:25,660 --> 00:22:26,620
It’s time

324
00:22:28,220 --> 00:22:30,140
to let them know my decision.

325
00:22:40,620 --> 00:22:41,780
When the fire started,

326
00:22:41,780 --> 00:22:42,860
we were all asleep.

327
00:22:43,140 --> 00:22:44,020
Once we smelled the smoke,

328
00:22:44,020 --> 00:22:45,100
the fire was already big.

329
00:22:45,340 --> 00:22:46,340
We pulled Princess

330
00:22:46,340 --> 00:22:47,340
out of the room,

331
00:22:47,580 --> 00:22:48,700
but she wet herself

332
00:22:48,700 --> 00:22:49,780
with oil,

333
00:22:50,100 --> 00:22:51,580
demanding to see you.

334
00:22:51,940 --> 00:22:54,020
Then Mr. Zhang sent someone to see His Majesty.

335
00:22:55,300 --> 00:22:56,820
Thank Heaven, you were allowed to come.

336
00:22:57,100 --> 00:22:59,060
Otherwise, it’d be a disaster.

337
00:23:02,060 --> 00:23:03,860
Mr. Liang! Mr. Liang!

338
00:23:04,820 --> 00:23:06,180
Mrs. Li is in danger!

339
00:23:06,340 --> 00:23:07,220
Come with me.

340
00:23:08,220 --> 00:23:09,180
Take care of Princess.

341
00:23:12,300 --> 00:23:13,940
Originally, Mrs. Li was waiting outside,

342
00:23:13,940 --> 00:23:14,620
but once she saw you,

343
00:23:14,620 --> 00:23:15,580
she looked annoyed.

344
00:23:16,220 --> 00:23:17,380
After you left with Princess,

345
00:23:17,380 --> 00:23:18,340
her annoyance grew.

346
00:23:18,620 --> 00:23:19,980
She started to cry in anger.

347
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:21,220
Then she probably became furious

348
00:23:21,220 --> 00:23:22,500
that she went inside

349
00:23:22,500 --> 00:23:23,780
and attempted to burn herself.

350
00:23:23,980 --> 00:23:24,860
Prince Consort rushed in

351
00:23:24,860 --> 00:23:25,940
and begged her to stop and come out

352
00:23:26,100 --> 00:23:26,940
but she was adamant

353
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:27,940
and refused to leave.

354
00:23:28,300 --> 00:23:30,020
You spineless coward!

355
00:23:30,220 --> 00:23:32,100
Mother, I’m begging you to stop!

356
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:33,140
You’re a wimp

357
00:23:33,860 --> 00:23:35,300
in front of your wife!

358
00:23:35,860 --> 00:23:37,500
Please stop, mother!

359
00:23:38,020 --> 00:23:38,900
I...

360
00:23:38,900 --> 00:23:39,740
Please, mother!

361
00:23:40,340 --> 00:23:42,780
I’m too ashamed to live!

362
00:23:42,780 --> 00:23:43,740
Stop, ma’am!

363
00:23:45,140 --> 00:23:45,860
Ma’am!

364
00:23:47,380 --> 00:23:49,020
I’d rather kill myself today

365
00:23:50,740 --> 00:23:51,580
than die in rage

366
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:54,460
because of you one day.

367
00:23:55,723 --> 00:23:56,936
Ma’am! Ma’am!

368
00:23:56,930 --> 00:23:57,586
Ma’am!

369
00:23:57,580 --> 00:23:59,623
- Ma’am, don’t do this! Be careful! - Ma’am!

370
00:23:59,700 --> 00:24:00,540
Mrs. Li!

371
00:24:00,780 --> 00:24:01,956
- Ma’am! - Ma’am!

372
00:24:01,950 --> 00:24:02,573
Ma’am!

373
00:24:06,700 --> 00:24:08,780
You disgusting sissy

374
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:11,740
are like those dirty monks

375
00:24:11,740 --> 00:24:13,500
trying to steal others’ wives.

376
00:24:15,100 --> 00:24:16,580
Even after I die,

377
00:24:17,340 --> 00:24:19,380
I’ll haunt you forever!

378
00:24:20,380 --> 00:24:21,700
I’ll make you pay.

379
00:24:22,420 --> 00:24:24,060
I’ll make you pay!

380
00:24:24,260 --> 00:24:25,140
Stop, ma’am!

381
00:24:25,140 --> 00:24:26,180
Please calm down, ma’am.

382
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:27,420
Stop, ma’am!

383
00:24:27,420 --> 00:24:28,420
- Please get out! - Ma’am!

384
00:24:28,460 --> 00:24:29,420
- Ma’am! - Don’t!

385
00:24:29,420 --> 00:24:30,060
Ma’am!

386
00:24:30,380 --> 00:24:31,060
Ma’am!

387
00:24:31,380 --> 00:24:32,940
- Ma’am! - Mother!

388
00:24:34,180 --> 00:24:35,220
I’ll make you pay!

389
00:24:35,220 --> 00:24:36,140
Calm down, ma’am.

390
00:24:36,340 --> 00:24:37,493
Please calm down.

391
00:24:37,743 --> 00:24:39,070
- Don’t! - Put out the fire.

392
00:24:39,100 --> 00:24:40,226
- Servants! Mother! - Put out the fire.

393
00:24:40,256 --> 00:24:41,410
Water. Go get water.

394
00:24:41,410 --> 00:24:42,306
Water. Hurry.

395
00:24:42,836 --> 00:24:43,663
Go! Go!

396
00:24:43,660 --> 00:24:44,996
- Put it out! - Ma’am!

397
00:24:45,236 --> 00:24:46,933
- Put it out! - Let’s go.

398
00:24:47,790 --> 00:24:48,786
Water!

399
00:25:06,660 --> 00:25:08,980
Are you here to see me take my last breath?

400
00:25:10,380 --> 00:25:11,100
Mother,

401
00:25:12,260 --> 00:25:13,340
just now, Mr. Liang

402
00:25:13,340 --> 00:25:14,940
risked his life to save you, mother.

403
00:25:15,460 --> 00:25:17,300
Because he was afraid!

404
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:26,620
You were afraid that if I died,

405
00:25:27,540 --> 00:25:28,540
His Majesty and officials

406
00:25:28,540 --> 00:25:29,740
would hold you accountable, right?

407
00:25:31,540 --> 00:25:32,900
Otherwise,

408
00:25:33,660 --> 00:25:34,660
considering how much you hate me,

409
00:25:35,700 --> 00:25:36,540
you’d rather see me

410
00:25:36,540 --> 00:25:38,140
be burned to ashes

411
00:25:39,380 --> 00:25:40,900
so that you and Princess

412
00:25:41,780 --> 00:25:43,260
could be together

413
00:25:44,060 --> 00:25:45,060
and enjoy the rest of your lives.

414
00:25:51,380 --> 00:25:52,380
I don’t hate you

415
00:25:53,900 --> 00:25:55,220
or others.

416
00:25:57,180 --> 00:25:58,980
I’m not sure

417
00:26:00,620 --> 00:26:01,740
why I went inside.

418
00:26:03,740 --> 00:26:04,820
But

419
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:06,140
had it been anyone else

420
00:26:06,140 --> 00:26:07,740
trapped in that room,

421
00:26:08,220 --> 00:26:09,300
I would’ve done the same

422
00:26:10,460 --> 00:26:12,220
whether it was you or not.

423
00:26:22,380 --> 00:26:23,820
So now,

424
00:26:24,460 --> 00:26:26,500
you’re on the moral high ground.

425
00:26:28,580 --> 00:26:29,900
You’re kind

426
00:26:30,580 --> 00:26:31,740
and have a heart of gold

427
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:34,700
while I’m evil and vicious

428
00:26:35,980 --> 00:26:37,780
who refuse to help you

429
00:26:38,260 --> 00:26:39,900
but keep pushing you.

430
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:41,820
I’m so harsh on you.

431
00:26:42,380 --> 00:26:43,900
How could you not hate me?

432
00:26:46,100 --> 00:26:47,740
I’m guilty beyond forgiveness.

433
00:26:50,580 --> 00:26:52,540
Were I blessed with children

434
00:26:53,940 --> 00:26:55,660
who were under this situation,

435
00:26:57,300 --> 00:26:58,660
I’d also hate

436
00:26:58,660 --> 00:27:00,220
that overreaching eunuch.

437
00:27:02,780 --> 00:27:04,260
You have every reason to resent me

438
00:27:05,100 --> 00:27:06,980
but I have no right to do the same to you.

439
00:27:10,340 --> 00:27:11,740
Do you think

440
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:13,980
I want to go this far

441
00:27:14,060 --> 00:27:16,100
and play the bad people here?

442
00:27:27,340 --> 00:27:29,020
My son is a good boy.

443
00:27:30,100 --> 00:27:31,420
He never complains

444
00:27:32,940 --> 00:27:35,100
about any unfair treatment

445
00:27:35,940 --> 00:27:38,220
but swallows his pride and suffers it in silence.

446
00:27:39,580 --> 00:27:41,060
As his mother,

447
00:27:41,340 --> 00:27:43,220
how could I just sit and do nothing?

448
00:27:46,700 --> 00:27:49,420
I know he isn’t a sweet talker.

449
00:27:50,420 --> 00:27:51,980
Princess doesn’t like him.

450
00:27:53,180 --> 00:27:54,060
Fine.

451
00:27:54,860 --> 00:27:55,900
We accept that.

452
00:27:57,980 --> 00:27:59,660
If all things fail,

453
00:28:00,860 --> 00:28:02,100
we can still put her on a pedestal

454
00:28:02,100 --> 00:28:04,220
and treat her with the highest courtesy.

455
00:28:06,220 --> 00:28:06,900
But

456
00:28:08,260 --> 00:28:10,220
she’s already married into our family.

457
00:28:11,260 --> 00:28:12,220
Actually,

458
00:28:12,860 --> 00:28:14,260
the world knows

459
00:28:14,260 --> 00:28:16,060
she married my son.

460
00:28:17,740 --> 00:28:18,740
You can

461
00:28:19,460 --> 00:28:20,460
stay indoors

462
00:28:20,460 --> 00:28:22,100
every day,

463
00:28:23,460 --> 00:28:26,100
but my son, a Prince Consort,

464
00:28:26,860 --> 00:28:28,980
has to go out to meet people.

465
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:36,180
He’s humble

466
00:28:37,380 --> 00:28:39,060
and always follows the rules

467
00:28:40,380 --> 00:28:42,300
throughout his life.

468
00:28:44,860 --> 00:28:45,980
But why

469
00:28:45,980 --> 00:28:48,140
does he have to endure such a humiliation

470
00:28:48,260 --> 00:28:49,980
and suffer so much?

471
00:28:57,820 --> 00:28:58,900
Mr. Liang,

472
00:29:00,900 --> 00:29:01,660
I know

473
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:04,020
you’re a kind man.

474
00:29:05,100 --> 00:29:07,780
You’re good-looking, considerate

475
00:29:08,660 --> 00:29:09,820
and educational.

476
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:12,500
Can you please talk to Princess nicely

477
00:29:13,100 --> 00:29:14,740
to stay away from you

478
00:29:15,540 --> 00:29:17,300
and stop causing trouble?

479
00:29:18,620 --> 00:29:20,340
All we want

480
00:29:21,060 --> 00:29:23,180
is to live peacefully.

481
00:29:24,820 --> 00:29:26,460
Please promise me.

482
00:29:27,580 --> 00:29:29,020
Please!

483
00:29:29,020 --> 00:29:30,820
Please keep a distance from her.

484
00:29:30,820 --> 00:29:31,540
Mother.

485
00:29:32,340 --> 00:29:34,563
Or my son’s life will be ruined.

486
00:29:34,590 --> 00:29:35,420
Mother.

487
00:29:35,860 --> 00:29:38,460
I’m begging you, Mr. Liang.

488
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:41,980
Mr. Liang.

489
00:29:45,420 --> 00:29:46,780
You’d better stay

490
00:29:48,180 --> 00:29:50,340
or Princess will be upset

491
00:29:51,700 --> 00:29:52,540
once she wakes up and doesn’t see you.

492
00:29:57,700 --> 00:29:58,580
Sima Guang,

493
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:01,740
many have tried to persuade me to summon

494
00:30:01,740 --> 00:30:03,020
imperial clansmen to the palace,

495
00:30:04,980 --> 00:30:06,300
but only you

496
00:30:06,700 --> 00:30:08,100
told me bluntly

497
00:30:09,380 --> 00:30:12,380
that my frequent illnesses this year

498
00:30:13,220 --> 00:30:15,060
have panicked the court.

499
00:30:15,700 --> 00:30:18,660
If anything happens to me

500
00:30:20,020 --> 00:30:21,780
before the heir is settled,

501
00:30:21,780 --> 00:30:22,820
crisis will arise.

502
00:30:25,140 --> 00:30:27,300
That remark is disrespectful

503
00:30:28,700 --> 00:30:30,100
but made out of loyalty.

504
00:30:33,220 --> 00:30:34,020
Alright.

505
00:30:35,060 --> 00:30:36,260
I can tell you now

506
00:30:38,420 --> 00:30:39,660
that I’ve already decided

507
00:30:40,500 --> 00:30:41,740
to summon Zongshi to the palace.

508
00:30:48,420 --> 00:30:50,420
I knew that speech

509
00:30:51,020 --> 00:30:52,140
could get me killed

510
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:54,740
but I didn’t expect

511
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:57,820
Your Majesty would take my advice.

512
00:30:59,220 --> 00:31:00,060
Kill you?

513
00:31:02,620 --> 00:31:04,020
That’ll make me the guilty one.

514
00:31:08,380 --> 00:31:10,300
Note my decision down

515
00:31:10,380 --> 00:31:11,860
for the Cabinet to deliberate.

516
00:31:15,220 --> 00:31:16,340
I believe Your Majesty should hold

517
00:31:16,580 --> 00:31:18,740
a formal discussion with ministers

518
00:31:18,740 --> 00:31:19,860
to address this matter.

519
00:31:24,900 --> 00:31:26,220
I’m a bit tired.

520
00:31:26,820 --> 00:31:29,860
Han Qi and I will discuss it another day.

521
00:31:53,180 --> 00:31:54,020
Minister Han.

522
00:31:59,780 --> 00:32:02,380
Censor Sima, you must be here for the salt tax.

523
00:32:02,980 --> 00:32:03,780
I’ll...

524
00:32:03,780 --> 00:32:04,700
That matter

525
00:32:04,820 --> 00:32:06,540
isn’t worth this visit.

526
00:32:09,940 --> 00:32:10,660
Then...

527
00:32:12,820 --> 00:32:14,180
I’m here

528
00:32:14,780 --> 00:32:17,060
for the future of the state.

529
00:32:25,500 --> 00:32:26,540
Has His Majesty decided

530
00:32:28,500 --> 00:32:29,860
to summon Zongshi to the palace?

531
00:32:32,980 --> 00:32:34,380
He nodded in agreement

532
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:36,580
but didn’t seem adamant.

533
00:32:37,620 --> 00:32:38,820
He said to have the Cabinet discuss it

534
00:32:38,820 --> 00:32:40,020
but didn’t issue the decree.

535
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:42,460
I was afraid

536
00:32:42,980 --> 00:32:44,900
it’d be put off indefinitely again.

537
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:47,260
So I insisted

538
00:32:47,340 --> 00:32:48,660
on His Majesty notifying the Cabinet

539
00:32:48,660 --> 00:32:50,020
in writing

540
00:32:50,780 --> 00:32:53,460
while coming here to deliver the message to you.

541
00:33:17,420 --> 00:33:18,820
Did you know

542
00:33:19,780 --> 00:33:20,740
Princess’s Mansion

543
00:33:21,580 --> 00:33:23,180
was on fire early this morning?

544
00:33:25,820 --> 00:33:27,380
I had an early meeting with His Majesty

545
00:33:28,020 --> 00:33:29,180
and knew nothing about that.

546
00:33:39,340 --> 00:33:40,940
A decree should be issued soon

547
00:33:41,220 --> 00:33:42,540
to summon Zongshi to the palace,

548
00:33:43,460 --> 00:33:46,300
or His Majesty may change his mind,

549
00:33:46,940 --> 00:33:48,820
speculations will rise

550
00:33:49,700 --> 00:33:52,340
and Zongshi will feel uneasy

551
00:33:52,660 --> 00:33:53,860
and have more doubts.

552
00:34:03,180 --> 00:34:03,980
Your Majesty,

553
00:34:05,700 --> 00:34:07,940
please allow Princess to keep Mr. Liang.

554
00:34:09,860 --> 00:34:10,940
My entire family

555
00:34:11,700 --> 00:34:13,180
won’t leak a word to others.

556
00:34:33,900 --> 00:34:35,060
I have one more request.

557
00:34:37,900 --> 00:34:38,660
What is it?

558
00:34:45,020 --> 00:34:47,020
Your Majesty, Your Highness, Madam Miao,

559
00:34:49,780 --> 00:34:51,260
please marry Jiaqing Zi to me

560
00:34:52,620 --> 00:34:53,340
as my concubine.

561
00:35:02,940 --> 00:35:04,420
I didn’t mean to set the place on fire.

562
00:35:05,420 --> 00:35:08,260
I woke up in the middle of the night.

563
00:35:09,180 --> 00:35:10,620
The candles were off. It was pitch dark.

564
00:35:12,100 --> 00:35:12,980
I got out of bed

565
00:35:13,500 --> 00:35:15,340
and felt like I was caged.

566
00:35:15,340 --> 00:35:16,620
There was no door.

567
00:35:17,700 --> 00:35:19,060
I was eager to get out

568
00:35:20,180 --> 00:35:22,660
so I took out the censer,

569
00:35:23,420 --> 00:35:24,700
opened it to use the incense

570
00:35:24,700 --> 00:35:26,300
to light the candles.

571
00:35:28,580 --> 00:35:29,700
Somehow,

572
00:35:30,900 --> 00:35:32,260
it didn’t work.

573
00:35:35,540 --> 00:35:38,500
Then I blew the incense,

574
00:35:40,100 --> 00:35:42,180
but the ash of it landed on the curtain

575
00:35:42,180 --> 00:35:43,260
and set it on fire.

576
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:46,780
Soon,

577
00:35:49,020 --> 00:35:52,020
the fire started to spread

578
00:35:52,980 --> 00:35:54,260
which made me strangely happy.

579
00:36:00,380 --> 00:36:04,460
Would I be able to see you

580
00:36:05,620 --> 00:36:07,300
once those walls were burned down?

581
00:36:10,100 --> 00:36:11,380
Princess,

582
00:36:12,380 --> 00:36:13,300
you should take good care of yourself.

583
00:36:14,020 --> 00:36:15,940
Don’t ever play with fire again.

584
00:36:17,700 --> 00:36:20,420
I just wanted to see you.

585
00:36:24,740 --> 00:36:25,660
Where’s Huirou?

586
00:36:26,420 --> 00:36:27,100
Huirou!

587
00:36:28,580 --> 00:36:29,260
Huirou!

588
00:36:38,780 --> 00:36:39,660
Let me see.

589
00:36:41,500 --> 00:36:42,660
Prince Consort asked His Majesty

590
00:36:42,780 --> 00:36:44,580
to allow you to stay here

591
00:36:44,580 --> 00:36:45,420
with Princess for now.

592
00:36:45,780 --> 00:36:46,820
His Majesty agreed.

593
00:36:47,620 --> 00:36:48,740
He also requested permission

594
00:36:49,140 --> 00:36:50,580
to marry Jiaqing Zi as his concubine.

595
00:37:00,580 --> 00:37:01,380
Master.

596
00:37:03,540 --> 00:37:04,900
Why aren’t you inside?

597
00:37:05,460 --> 00:37:07,780
His Majesty wished to be alone

598
00:37:08,100 --> 00:37:09,340
to think quietly.

599
00:37:15,060 --> 00:37:15,860
Your Majesty.

600
00:37:46,940 --> 00:37:47,740
There you are.

601
00:37:50,860 --> 00:37:51,660
Your Majesty.

602
00:37:55,300 --> 00:37:56,580
How’s Zongshi?

603
00:37:58,940 --> 00:37:59,660
Good.

604
00:38:00,580 --> 00:38:03,060
But not as good as Your Majesty.

605
00:38:09,220 --> 00:38:10,020
Well said.

606
00:38:10,860 --> 00:38:13,460
I thought you’d say,

607
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:15,900
“I’m too humble to judge”.

608
00:38:24,780 --> 00:38:26,020
Zongshi is good.

609
00:38:27,060 --> 00:38:28,660
Officials all believe

610
00:38:29,740 --> 00:38:32,380
he’s most likely to be in line to the throne.

611
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:34,540
But without an official title,

612
00:38:35,180 --> 00:38:36,540
it’s understandable

613
00:38:38,020 --> 00:38:39,860
that he feels uneasy.

614
00:38:42,020 --> 00:38:43,900
Even my own son

615
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:45,580
might not

616
00:38:45,580 --> 00:38:46,860
outperform him.

617
00:38:49,980 --> 00:38:51,140
It is what it is now.

618
00:38:53,980 --> 00:38:55,260
Once I’m gone,

619
00:38:55,460 --> 00:38:58,340
he’ll no longer have doubts.

620
00:39:03,820 --> 00:39:05,140
Sons of royalty

621
00:39:06,980 --> 00:39:10,020
headed the Court of the Imperial Clan before.

622
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:13,900
Issue a decree tomorrow

623
00:39:14,500 --> 00:39:16,340
to appoint Zongshi Chief of the Imperial Clan.

624
00:39:16,900 --> 00:39:17,620
Yes.

625
00:39:19,100 --> 00:39:20,620
That way,

626
00:39:21,460 --> 00:39:22,980
officials will all know my answer.

627
00:39:27,980 --> 00:39:31,380
Jiaqing Zi, we grew up together.

628
00:39:32,100 --> 00:39:33,300
Although you’re my maid,

629
00:39:33,860 --> 00:39:35,060
I regard you

630
00:39:35,340 --> 00:39:36,660
as my sister.

631
00:39:38,020 --> 00:39:38,900
Don’t worry.

632
00:39:40,020 --> 00:39:41,860
I won’t sacrifice you for my happiness.

633
00:39:42,780 --> 00:39:44,220
I’ll tell father

634
00:39:44,900 --> 00:39:46,580
that you won’t be Li Wei’s concubine.

635
00:39:48,340 --> 00:39:50,820
No, I’m willing to marry him.

636
00:39:54,660 --> 00:39:55,700
You’re so nice to me.

637
00:39:56,420 --> 00:39:58,660
I won’t allow you to suffer for me.

638
00:40:01,500 --> 00:40:02,620
Maybe to you,

639
00:40:03,540 --> 00:40:05,140
his love and care only make you suffer,

640
00:40:06,300 --> 00:40:07,620
but in my eyes,

641
00:40:08,020 --> 00:40:09,460
as long as I can be with him every day,

642
00:40:10,260 --> 00:40:11,140
even if

643
00:40:11,140 --> 00:40:12,340
he’ll never love me back,

644
00:40:12,620 --> 00:40:13,780
I’ll feel more than content.

645
00:40:16,340 --> 00:40:17,020
What...

646
00:40:18,420 --> 00:40:19,260
do you mean?

647
00:40:24,540 --> 00:40:25,660
I love him.

648
00:40:29,180 --> 00:40:29,940
You love...

649
00:40:31,340 --> 00:40:32,140
Li Wei?

650
00:40:35,180 --> 00:40:37,060
Just because you despise him,

651
00:40:38,140 --> 00:40:40,020
he can’t be loved by others?

652
00:40:41,740 --> 00:40:42,860
He’s an unparalleled artist

653
00:40:43,380 --> 00:40:44,780
but he never takes pride in that.

654
00:40:46,220 --> 00:40:47,660
Art is his tool

655
00:40:48,740 --> 00:40:50,300
to outpour his sorrow,

656
00:40:51,220 --> 00:40:52,580
drive his loneliness away

657
00:40:53,180 --> 00:40:54,580
and express his happiness.

658
00:40:55,820 --> 00:40:57,020
When others don’t understand him,

659
00:40:57,580 --> 00:40:58,660
he isn’t upset.

660
00:40:59,380 --> 00:41:00,540
When they look down on him,

661
00:41:00,780 --> 00:41:01,860
he holds no grudge.

662
00:41:02,860 --> 00:41:04,100
He’s the kindest,

663
00:41:04,300 --> 00:41:06,780
gentlest

664
00:41:06,820 --> 00:41:08,140
and most tolerant man I’ve ever seen.

665
00:41:11,180 --> 00:41:14,020
I can’t help falling in love with him.

666
00:41:14,780 --> 00:41:15,900
I’m guilty.

667
00:41:16,580 --> 00:41:17,740
Please punish me.

668
00:41:29,780 --> 00:41:33,620
Jiaqing Zi, I envy you so much

669
00:41:35,460 --> 00:41:37,100
that you can spend the rest of your life

670
00:41:38,020 --> 00:41:38,900
with your love

671
00:41:39,900 --> 00:41:41,820
in front of everyone.

672
00:42:01,460 --> 00:42:08,460
♪ Memory is the breath of deep sleep ♪

673
00:42:09,020 --> 00:42:15,900
♪ It emerges in every crevice ♪

674
00:42:16,380 --> 00:42:22,740
♪ Shallow dreams are like
copper bells under eaves ♪

675
00:42:23,180 --> 00:42:29,940
♪ Woken up when the wind blows ♪

676
00:42:31,180 --> 00:42:37,980
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

677
00:42:38,580 --> 00:42:45,340
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

678
00:42:45,900 --> 00:42:52,940
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

679
00:42:52,940 --> 00:42:59,740
♪ Regardless of the ending ♪

680
00:43:04,620 --> 00:43:08,140
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

681
00:43:08,340 --> 00:43:11,940
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

682
00:43:11,940 --> 00:43:15,140
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

683
00:43:15,140 --> 00:43:19,540
♪ He plays with the butterfly, gathering honey ♪

684
00:43:19,540 --> 00:43:23,260
♪ Peach blossoms tell a love story ♪

685
00:43:23,260 --> 00:43:26,820
♪ About a couple who lives happily ♪

686
00:43:26,820 --> 00:43:30,540
♪ Unluckily deep love comes to nowhere ♪

687
00:43:30,540 --> 00:43:36,300
♪ All fated,
drawing Double Happiness in autumn ♪

